**CI/Quality parity complete**
## Changes Summary

| File | Change |
|------|--------|
| `scripts/validate.py` | **New** - Shared validation script (7 checks) |
| `.github/workflows/ci.yml` | Refactored to use shared script |
| `Makefile` | Added `ci`, `quality`, `lint`, and `validate-*` targets |
| `plugins/zircote/.claude-plugin/plugin.json` | Removed invalid commands reference |
| `plugins/gh/commands/review-comments.md` | **New** - PR review command |
| `plugins/gh/.claude-plugin/plugin.json` | Registered new command, v0.4.0 |
| `plugins/gh/{CHANGELOG,README}.md` | Updated docs |

## New Make Targets

```
make ci                  # Run all CI checks (same as GitHub Actions)
make quality             # Alias for ci
make lint                # Run linting checks
make validate            # Run all plugin validations
make validate-json       # Validate JSON syntax only
make validate-fields     # Check required fields only
make validate-version    # Validate semantic versions only
make validate-readme     # Check README files exist
make validate-commands   # Validate command file references
make validate-agents     # Validate agent file references
make validate-skills     # Validate skill file references
```

